<h1 align="center">🌐 HealthNest – Revolutionizing Telemedicine</h1>

<p align="center">
HealthNest is a modern, full-featured telehealth platform offering seamless virtual care. Built with Next.js, Node.js, and Supabase, it empowers patients, doctors, and admins with real-time communication, secure records, and smart appointment systems.
</p>

---

## 🚀 Key Features  

- 👥 **Role-Based Access Control**  
  - **Patients**: Book consultations, chat with doctors, access prescriptions  
  - **Doctors**: Manage availability, view patient records, video consultations  
  - **Admins**: Monitor platform, manage users & appointments  

- 🩺 **HIPAA-Compliant Video Calls**  
- 📅 **Smart Appointment Booking**  
- 💬 **Real-time Chat System**  
- 📁 **Medical Record Upload & Access**  
- 💊 **E-Prescriptions** Generation  
- 💳 **Integrated Payments & Insurance Check**  
- 🤖 **AI Symptom Checker Bot**  
- 📊 **Dashboards** for Patients, Doctors & Admins  

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack  

- **Frontend**: [Next.js](https://nextjs.org/) + [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)  
- **Backend**: [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) + [Express.js](https://expressjs.com/)  
- **Database**: [Supabase](https://supabase.io/) – HIPAA-compliant PostgreSQL  
- **Authentication**: Supabase Auth / Firebase Auth  
- **Video Calls**: [WebRTC](https://webrtc.org/) / [Twilio](https://www.twilio.com/) / [Agora](https://www.agora.io/)  
- **Payments**: [Stripe](https://stripe.com/) / [PayPal](https://paypal.com)  
- **Hosting**: [Vercel](https://vercel.com/) / AWS  

---

## 👨‍⚕️ User Roles & Dashboards  

### 👤 Patient Portal  
- 📋 View medical history & prescriptions  
- 📅 Book virtual appointments  
- 📁 Upload test reports  
- 💬 Secure chat with doctors  
- 💳 Manage payments & insurance  

### 🩺 Doctor Dashboard  
- 🗓 Manage schedule & availability  
- 📞 Join video consultations  
- 📁 Access patient health records  
- 💊 Generate & send e-prescriptions  
- 📈 Track earnings & consultations  

### 🛠️ Admin Panel  
- 📊 Analytics dashboard  
- 👥 Manage users (patients & doctors)  
- 📅 Monitor all appointments  
- 💰 Oversee payments and system health  
- ⚙️ Platform configuration  

